snippet.title: EverQuest II Age of Discovery Expansion [OFFICIAL TRAILER]
snippet.description: Welcome to EverQuest II® Age of Discovery™! This is the eighth expansion of the groundbreaking EverQuest II franchise. This is truly an unprecedented expansion in terms of pure features and  valuable in-game items.
